### Revenue Trend (Pro)

| Bucket | Source | Revenue Formula | Booking Count | Fill Rate | Game Filter |
|--------|--------|----------------|---------------|-----------|------------|
| Daily (≤30d) | bookings + games | SUM(club_payout_cents) WHERE payment_method='stripe', confirmed | SUM(confirmed) | SUM(conf)/SUM(spots) | past games only (date_time <= now()) |
| Weekly (>30d) | bookings + games | Same, DATE_TRUNC('week') | Same | Same | past games only |

Trend chart sums reconcile exactly with KPI totals for the same period — both filter `date_time <= now()`.

### Top Games (Pro)

Filters: past games (date_time < now()), non-cancelled, within p_days.
Ordered by: confirmed_count DESC, fill_rate DESC. Top 5.
Revenue = club_payout_cents (net), Stripe only.

### Peak Times (Pro)

Groups past games by DOW + hour. AVG(confirmed_count) per slot. Top 5 by avg_confirmed DESC.

