## Revenue Formulas

```
Gross Revenue     = SUM(platform_fee_cents + club_payout_cents)  [Stripe confirmed]
Platform Fee      = SUM(platform_fee_cents)                       [Stripe confirmed]
Club Net Payout   = SUM(club_payout_cents)                        [Stripe confirmed]
Credits Used      = SUM(credits_applied_cents)                    [all confirmed — Stripe + credit-only]
Refunded          = SUM(platform_fee_cents + club_payout_cents)   [cancelled + fee_paid=true + Stripe]
Free Booking Rev  = $0 (counts as booking, never as revenue)
```

Invariant: `Gross Revenue - Platform Fee = Club Net Payout` (for Stripe bookings).
Invariant: `Credits Used` and `Gross Revenue` are mutually independent — credits on Stripe bookings are already counted in Credits Used via credits_applied_cents; the Stripe portion is in Gross.

