## Booking State Transitions — Analytics Impact

| Transition | Revenue Impact | Booking Count | Credits |
|-----------|---------------|---------------|---------|
| waitlisted → confirmed (free) | None | +1 confirmed | None |
| waitlisted → confirmed (Stripe) | +gross at payment time | +1 confirmed | None |
| waitlisted → confirmed (credits only) | None | +1 confirmed, +1 free | +credits_applied |
| confirmed (Stripe) → cancelled | -gross moves to Refunded | -1 confirmed | Refunded to player_credits |
| confirmed (Stripe, < 6h window) → cancelled | -gross moves to Refunded | -1 confirmed | No credit issued |
| confirmed (credit-only) → cancelled (> 6h) | None | -1 confirmed | Credits restored to player_credits |
| cancelled game | All bookings excluded (games.status='cancelled' filter) | 0 | N/A |

Idempotency: The `Refunded` metric counts cancelled bookings (status='cancelled') — not credits issued. A booking cancelled twice is impossible (status can only move to cancelled once). Double-counting cannot occur.

