## Phase 5A Dead Code

`get_club_revenue_summary` and `get_club_fill_rate_summary` RPCs (migrations 20260406_*) exist in the DB and are implemented in SupabaseService + AppState (`revenueSummaryByClubID`, `fillRateSummaryByClubID`), but are NOT called from any view. These are Phase 5A artifacts fully superseded by Phase 5B RPCs. Safe to ignore; do not wire them up — they lack the credits and refunded metrics added in Phase 5B.

