## Access Control (defense-in-depth)

1. **iOS FeatureGateService** — blocks non-Pro users at the view layer; shows demo data
2. **AppState.fetchClubAdvancedAnalytics** — skips fetch when `analyticsLocked`
3. **SQL SECURITY DEFINER functions** — enforce owner/admin check + analytics_access entitlement before touching any row
4. **RLS** — bookings, games, club_members have RLS; SECURITY DEFINER bypasses RLS but applies its own explicit auth checks

### Entitlement source chain (authoritative order)

1. `club_subscriptions.plan_type + status` — Stripe-managed, set by stripe-webhook Edge Function
2. `clubs.subscription_tier` — denormalized fallback; written only by service_role Edge Functions; used by `derive_club_entitlements` when no active Stripe subscription row exists
3. `club_entitlements` table — output of `derive_club_entitlements`; the only table iOS reads
4. `AppState.entitlementsByClubID` — in-memory cache; populated by `fetchClubEntitlements` on dashboard open + subscription actions + foreground return

